      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3, a true benchmark of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with a recently performed valve adjustment and a reinforced rear subframe to address chassis rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its showroom luster with original factory paint thickness, while the underside remains free of any oxidation or fluid seepage. Upgraded with Bilstein PSS10 dampers for enhanced rebound and compression control, this vehicle offers a tactile, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare. A collector-grade specimen for the automotive purist.",
